result:
<!-- 新增弹框 -->
      <a-modal
      title="新建"
      style="top: 20px;"
      :width="600"
      v-model="visible"
      @ok="handleSubmit"
    >
    <a-form :form="form">
      <a-form-item
        label="名称"
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
        <a-input
          v-decorator="[
            'name',
            {rules: [{ required: true, message: '请输入名称' }]}
          ]"
          placeholder="名称" />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        label="版本号"
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
        <a-input
          v-decorator="[
            'appVersion',
            {rules: [{ required: true, message: '请输入版本号' }]}
          ]"
          placeholder="版本号"
           />
      </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
        label="描述"
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
        <a-textarea
           placeholder="请输入描述" :rows="4"
          v-decorator="[
            'contents',
            {rules: [{ message: '请输入描述' }]}
          ]"
        />
      </a-form-item>
       <a-form-item
        label="上传"
        :labelCol="labelCol"
        :wrapperCol="wrapperCol"
        >
<!--      <a-upload name="file" :multiple="false" action="http://robot.lovechuangchuang.com:8085/AppManage/fileUpload" :fileList="fileList" :headers="headers" @change="handleChange">-->
      <a-upload name="file" :multiple="false" action="http://192.168.1.110:54321/AppManage/fileUpload" :fileList="fileList" :headers="headers" @change="handleChange">
        <a-button>
          <a-icon type="upload" /> 点击上传
        </a-button>
      </a-upload>
      </a-form-item>
    </a-form>
    </a-modal>
